{"title":"POC’s Ventral Light Helmet Weighs in at Just 270g","link":"https://theradavist.com/2021/02/pocs-ventral-light-helmet-weighs-in-at-just-270g/?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pocs-ventral-light-helmet-weighs-in-at-just-270g","date":1614092385000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section><article id=\"article-206169\"><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" alt=\"POC’s Ventral Light Helmet Weighs in at Just 270g\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://radavist-static-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w,https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p></div><header><h4>Radar</h4></header><div><p><img src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" data-base-url=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png\" data-base-quality=\"75\" data-alt-srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2021/02/PocVENTRAL-LITE.png?w=2000&amp;quality=75\"></p><p>There’s <a href=\"http://www.bluebulbprojects.com/MeasureOfThings/results.php?comp=weight&amp;unit=gms&amp;amt=270&amp;sort=cntD&amp;p=5\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">this website</a> that offers up weight comparisons. For instance, you can put in 270g and it will tell you what weighs about that or by what multitude. For instance, 270g is about three times the weight of a deck of cards. Or, my personal favorite, 270g is about the weight of an adult hamster.</p><p>Having light-weight gear is a <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/2020/10/condensare-packlist-baileys-mone-hardtail-29er-packed-for-touring-the-northern-new-mexico-cdt/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">game we all like to play</a> and having a light helmet might just make you want to wear it even more, which is a good measure when it comes to something that can save your life. The new POC Ventral Light helmet shaves the unnecessary grams without compromising your safety.</p><p>It’s the weight of a hamster on your head, with a retail of $275. See more at <a href=\"https://na.pocsports.com/products/ventral-lite\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">POC</a>.</p></div><nav><h4>Related</h4></nav></article></section></div>","author":"prolly","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"e67686411f6d57a28d6a26f2e9bdff78d69cca06db012ecbc28a77ee3ce66f3f","category":"Cycling"}